    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >传奇制作人 “吹哥” Jonathan Blow（代表作：《时空幻境》《见证者》）携新作《沉星之序》重磅归来。这款宏大的冒险游戏内含 1000 多个手工设计的谜题，旨在考验你的智慧极限。你将踏入充满奇异魔法、危险机关与凶残怪物的异界，探索四个机制迥异、角色鲜明、故事独立的平行世界，最终见证它们彼此交汇碰撞的壮丽景象。随着世界融合、角色相遇，谜题系统也将相互交织，催生出意想不到的全新玩法。按自己的节奏自由探索，随时重返各个世界与挑战。解锁独特的可操作角色，掌握不断演变的游戏机制，逐步剥开这片广阔互联世界的深层秘密。融合探索、叙事与持续蜕变的机制，《沉星之序》将为你呈现一场前所未有、充满生命力的谜境之旅。  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >数千谜题，交织成篇</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上这场创意十足的谜题冒险，体验数十种游戏机制与数百小时的独特玩法。每一个谜题都承前启后，引入全新机制，回报你的好奇心与坚持。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/499170/extras/fcbaa6b2574a1c56b06bcf9cc4034a2e.poster.avif?t=1771582260\" width=616 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/499170/extras/fcbaa6b2574a1c56b06bcf9cc4034a2e.webm?t=1771582260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自由探索，随心漫游</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索四个庞大而神秘的世界，每个世界都有专属的角色、规则、险境与待发掘的秘密。来去随心，按自己的节奏应对眼前的一切谜题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/499170/extras/b6ee0437f3be077902bfe9a6ec0f8022.poster.avif?t=1771582260\" width=616 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/499170/extras/b6ee0437f3be077902bfe9a6ec0f8022.webm?t=1771582260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >化身风格迥异的英雄</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >女王、盗贼、战士、巫师、乃至一艘会说话的小船……都将是这段传奇的英雄。每位角色都拥有相辅相成的能力与引人入胜的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/499170/extras/8f42bea0d7f9ac7203b868dba18ee640.poster.avif?t=1771582260\" width=616 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/499170/extras/8f42bea0d7f9ac7203b868dba18ee640.webm?t=1771582260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >破解史诗级的谜团</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着角色相遇、世界相互碰撞，谜团逐渐揭晓。通过谜题与收集散落的笔记，你将一步步深入了解这个神秘国度。借助每一条线索、每一片拼图，最终揭开《沉星之序》的终极秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/499170/extras/68fb435f74af24c2a13b486dc967fd6c.poster.avif?t=1771582260\" width=616 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/499170/extras/68fb435f74af24c2a13b486dc967fd6c.webm?t=1771582260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
